import "./App.css"
import Header from './components/Heading/Header'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from "./components/home/hero/Home"


const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
      <Header />
        <Switch>
          <Route path ='/' exact component={Home}/>
        </Switch>       
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
